# Project Checklist

## 1. Project Setup & Dependencies
-------------------------------------------------
### 1. Initial Setup
- [ ] Create new Next.js project with TypeScript
- [ ] Configure project structure (/app, /components, /lib, etc.)
- [ ] Initialize Git repository
- [ ] Create .gitignore file

### 2. UI Development - Core Dependencies
- [ ] Install and configure Tailwind CSS
- [ ] Set up shadcn/ui components
- [ ] Install Lucide icons
- [ ] Configure ESLint and Prettier
- [ ] Set up TypeScript configuration
- [ ] Install development dependencies (testing libraries, etc.)

### 3. Environment Configuration
- [ ] Create development environment (.env.development)
- [ ] Create production environment (.env.production)
- [ ] Set up environment variable validation
- [ ] Document all environment variables

### 4. Design System
- [ ] Set up color palette in Tailwind config
- [ ] Create typography system
- [ ] Define spacing/sizing scales
- [ ] Create reusable button styles
- [ ] Define form component styles
- [ ] Create animation utilities

## 2. Accessibility
-------------------------------------------------
- [ ] Implement keyboard navigation
- [ ] Add ARIA labels and roles
- [ ] Ensure proper heading hierarchy
- [ ] Test with screen readers
- [ ] Add skip-to-main content link
- [ ] Implement focus management

## 3. Page Development
-------------------------------------------------
### * Core Pages
- [ ] Create homepage layout
- [ ] Build about page
- [ ] Implement contact page
- [ ] Create privacy policy page
- [ ] Build terms of service page
- [ ] Design 404 error page

### * Dynamic Pages
- [ ] Set up dynamic routing
- [ ] Implement loading states
- [ ] Create error handling
- [ ] Add pagination (if needed)
- [ ] Configure data fetching
- [ ] Implement caching strategy

## 4. Deployment & Infrastructure
-------------------------------------------------
### * Development Environment
- [ ] Set up local development workflow
- [ ] Configure hot reloading
- [ ] Set up development database
- [ ] Create development API endpoints

### * Production Deployment
- [ ] Configure Cloudflare Pages
- [ ] Set up custom domain
- [ ] Configure SSL certificates
- [ ] Set up CDN caching

### * SEO & Metadata
#### Basic SEO
- [ ] Create robots.txt
- [ ] Generate sitemap.xml
- [ ] Configure canonical URLs
- [ ] Set up metadata components
- [ ] Implement JSON-LD schemas
- [ ] Add alt tags to images

#### Advanced SEO
- [ ] Configure Open Graph tags
- [ ] Set up Twitter Cards
- [ ] Implement structured data
- [ ] Create meta descriptions

### * Error Handling
#### Client-Side Errors
- [ ] Implement error boundaries
- [ ] Create error logging system
- [ ] Design error UI components
- [ ] Handle network errors
- [ ] Manage state errors
- [ ] Handle form validation errors

#### Server-Side Errors
- [ ] Set up API error handling
- [ ] Create error logging system
- [ ] Implement rate limiting
- [ ] Handle database errors
- [ ] Create custom error pages
- [ ] Configure error notifications

## 7. Analytics & Tracking
-------------------------------------------------
### Setup
- [ ] Create GTM container
- [ ] Configure data layer
- [ ] Set up custom events
- [ ] Implement page tracking
- [ ] Configure form tracking
- [ ] Set up conversion tracking

### Monitoring
- [ ] Configure performance monitoring
- [ ] Track Core Web Vitals
- [ ] Monitor load times
- [ ] Set up alerts

## 8. Internationalization
-------------------------------------------------
### Basic Setup
- [ ] Configure language detection
- [ ] Set up translation files
- [ ] Implement language switcher
- [ ] Create translation utilities
- [ ] Set up default language
- [ ] Configure fallback languages

### RTL Support
- [ ] Create direction utilities
- [ ] Implement RTL styles
- [ ] Test RTL layouts
- [ ] Configure RTL switching
- [ ] Test bi-directional text
- [ ] Verify RTL components

## 9. Performance Optimization
-------------------------------------------------
### Code Optimization
- [ ] Implement code splitting
- [ ] Configure lazy loading
- [ ] Optimize bundle size
- [ ] Minimize CSS
- [ ] Configure tree shaking
- [ ] Implement debouncing/throttling

### Asset Optimization
- [ ] Optimize images
- [ ] Configure font loading
- [ ] Minimize JavaScript
- [ ] Set up asset caching
- [ ] Configure compression
- [ ] Implement preloading

## 10. Security
-------------------------------------------------
### Basic Security
- [ ] Implement CSRF protection
- [ ] Configure XSS prevention
- [ ] Set up Content Security Policy
- [ ] Configure secure headers
- [ ] Implement rate limiting
- [ ] Set up password policies

### Advanced Security
- [ ] Configure authentication
- [ ] Set up authorization
- [ ] Implement API security
- [ ] Configure session management
- [ ] Set up audit logging
- [ ] Implement data encryption

## 11. Testing
-------------------------------------------------
### Unit Tests
- [ ] Set up testing framework
- [ ] Create component tests
- [ ] Test utility functions
- [ ] Test hooks
- [ ] Test state management
- [ ] Create mock services

### Integration Tests
- [ ] Test component interactions
- [ ] Validate API calls
- [ ] Ensure proper data flow
- [ ] Test routing behavior

### End-to-End (E2E) Tests
- [ ] Simulate user journeys
- [ ] Test critical workflows
- [ ] Validate form submissions
- [ ] Ensure error handling correctness

### Regression Testing
- [ ] Automate regression tests
- [ ] Run tests on every deployment
- [ ] Monitor test coverage
- [ ] Identify and fix regressions

## 12. Documentation
-------------------------------------------------
### Project Documentation
- [ ] Write README file
- [ ] Document project structure
- [ ] Provide setup instructions
- [ ] Include contribution guidelines

### API Documentation
- [ ] Generate API documentation
- [ ] Describe endpoints and parameters
- [ ] Provide example requests/responses
- [ ] Include authentication details

### User Documentation
- [ ] Create user guides
- [ ] Write FAQ section
- [ ] Provide troubleshooting tips
- [ ] Include contact information
